title: TFW Jhin thinks he is a bird
body:
https://youtu.be/yEzRn1ft4Wg?t=23m37s

I died... this is so funny and sad at the same time... lol tbh, this is down right meme worthy

also I know, thread about youtube video with no substance. i will take my downvotes, but it is queued  up to start at the right spot, so at least i was nice :p
